Description: word-sys's PDF Editor - Simple PDF Text Editor
 word-sys's PDF Editor allows users to open PDF files, view pages, select
 existing text blocks, modify or delete them, and add new text blocks.
 It focuses on simple text content manipulation rather than full PDF
 annotation or structural changes. It can also export to DOCX, PPTX, ODP (requires
 LibreOffice) and TXT formats.
